messages.text: have you packed your bag yet?
not yet. I had the last wedding dress fitting this morning.
you must look lovely in your wedding dress
I don’t care what I look like in my wedding dress.
the drive will take about one night and one day.
so make sure you bring all you need. Toiletries, underwear, etc.
of course…
a few minutes later
how are you getting on?
very well. I saw the House of Correction yesterday
right
and Isaiah is taking me on a private tour of the Trinity soon
that’s a great honor
I don’t know what the Trinity is
it’s our sacred building
it’s divided into three parts: Body (a storage for money and supplies)
Memory (a portrait gallery of important people)
and Soul. That’s the main part. It’s a sanctuary for religious ceremonies.
it’s where I’m supposed to get married…
I can’t wait to see it all
I’m going
good luck then
a little bit later
The funeral is happening next Monday.
I’ll be there.
when are you leaving?
at midnight tonight
really?
Nazarene’s wedding is scheduled for tomorrow
looking forward to seeing you
how are you feeling about what I told you yesterday?
determined to find my biological father
I’ve always felt that I didn’t truly belong in our family anyway
but I don’t want to go there now
whatever you feel is best
did you collect enough material about the cult?
no, to be honest
but Nazarene wants to leave at all costs
I bet
where will you take her?
haven’t thought of that. I guess she’ll live with me for a while
I wish I could stay more
every day here brings something new
what have you done today?
Isaiah showed me their sacred building
this is the main room
there was also a gallery of past leaders and important people in the sect
this is a photo of Lord Isiaiah
Jesus! He looks like a proper psychopath
believe it or not he’s actually quite nice
may I remind you that the reason why you’re there...
is because that guy wants to rape a kid?
marry her
and may I remind you that I’m driving away with her tonight?
yeah ok
there’s something else
something else what?
it’s really weird
he showed me the portrait of this girl
they call her the Holy Virgin.
Basically she won the beauty pageant at the Holy Wedding Celebrations
so, you know, she was going to be burned at the stake to become God’s wife
but when they were about to light the fire she gave birth to a child
the son of God therefore
okay. This isn’t any weirder than a lot of stuff you’ve told me before
I haven’t shown you the portrait
:O
are you thinking what I’m thinking?
yes. She looks like Mum.
well I mean it’s hard to tell...
bc it’s just a painting and the girl is so young
but she looks like Mum
what happened to her?
she disappeared. That’s all I know
so weird
should I ask for more details?
no no leave it please
who knows what they might think
it’s obviously a coincidence
later that night
have you left?
in the process
I said I was taking a late night walk in town.
I’m in the car waiting for Nazarene
will they not get suspicious?
I left practically all my stuff in the room
only took wallet, keys, and an extra jumper
good luck brother. Let me know where you’re on your way
at midnight
are you out?
in bed. I can still hear Father and his wife talking in the room next door
you mean your mum?
no, his second wife. Mother sleeps in the basement.
there isn’t enough space for everyone in the house.
Father gives the best rooms to his favourites wives
I see
are you ready for a new life?
I will miss Mother
I wish I could take her away with me
why not?
she believes in this place despite everything
she’s miserable but she thinks she’ll be rewarded one day for her suffering
once I told her I’d rather live alone on the street than with my uncle
she gave me a look that scared me
if she had any idea what I’m up to I know she’d go straight to Father
I guess she thinks staying at Weeping Rock is what’s best for you
she does
she means well
I know
they’ve stopped talking
Father is snoring
get out quick
oh no wait
baby Grace is crying
my new sister
how many children live in that house?
my Mother has eight, Mother Jemima has nine and Mother Ruth three
someone’s moving in the house
it must be Mother Ruth going to feed Grace
it will take a little while
I’m going now
quick
it’s locked!!
what’s locked?
my door!
from the outside!!
they found out you were going to run away??
I don’t know!!
maybe Mother guessed I would try something like that
get out through the window
my room is on the third floor
use your sheets to make a rope
it won’t reach the ground
a little jump won’t kill you
okay
oh no no no no!!!
what??
my brother Daniel is beneath my window
doing what?
keeping guard!
oh shit. They know!
they know about me too then!
if they did they would have locked you up
my family know I don’t want this wedding
they outguessed me
what am I going to do?
don’t abandon me now
I won’t! I’ll come to your wedding tomorrow
smile, look happy
I’ll keep a close watch on you
and then?
and then I’ll improvise something
